name: e9Art - the many faces of AI

metadata.name: AI Faces #01
metadata.description:
one of my favorite things about AI art is that it’s unexpected. 

thus fulfilling my major life-goals and my purpose in art: childlike WONDER joyful SURPRISE, playful ADVENTURE and meaningful PURPOSE.

and yes, it IS meaningful, if for no other reason than it satisfies my life-goals. but also, i’m learning new things, it’s helping me grow, it’s part of my education and practice. 

in other words, it’s making me a better artist. 

AI is a tool in my artist’s toolbox, like a camera, or perhaps like photoshop. and it comes with a variety of methods of fine-tuning, allowing me to manipulate the end results.

but also … because of its random and unpredictable nature ... it somehow adds to, and becomes part of, my INTUITIVE process. 

not to mention it’s fun as hell, a wild-ride and i’m having the time of my life. it’s a playground for my imagination. an amusement park full of fun and thrills that changes by the minute … 

digital 1/1 art by e9Art using VQgan-Clip, April 2022 … 10000x10000
